{"tid":376092,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"如果有一天你可以忘掉過去，記得來找我","createTime":"2017-08-26T19:12:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-27T15:35:31.000Z","uid":13909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"acd8b081918f463343bef33573c322e6c1493688","tid":376092,"uid":13909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T19:12:45.000Z","msg":"我很快就適應了這種生活，雖然有時只是逢場作戲，雖然有許多只是霧水情緣，不過沒關係了，哪來那麼多一生一世。"},{"pid":"bb1cdf0d70db1add30a6a3a460ed24c06fcb890d","tid":376092,"uid":89134,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T19:15:06.000Z","msg":"有一天晚上<br />\n夢一場<br />\n你白髮蒼蒼說帶我流浪<br />\n我還是沒猶豫就隨你去天堂"},{"pid":"8ae8b54553511fcaacfcfc7abc32e81ec12471ca","tid":376092,"uid":13909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T20:00:40.000Z","msg":"我曾經愛上一個人，我想知道她到底喜不喜歡我。我發現這個機器人很像她，我開始嘗試在她身上尋找答案。"},{"pid":"7475490e0e2b752bbd723b993ad5f63eb31041ab","tid":376092,"uid":13909,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T20:33:13.000Z","msg":"我不斷的嘗試，但她始終沒有反應。在我最失望的時候我想過放棄，可很快我又繼續，<br />\n。慢慢的，我開始懷疑自己。"},{"pid":"0042b2d3e876e78aa63e316fb4cd035700d8023b","tid":376092,"uid":10084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T23:27:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f64359ea6a5c2e972b685fa697b5023143c7d8cb","tid":376092,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T03:34:15.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"e040fa2273e200772caa545e4607ee0d173a9137","tid":376092,"uid":13909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T15:35:31.000Z","msg":"她對你沒有反應未必是因為它反映遲鈍，也許是因為她對你沒有感覺。<br />\n到最後終於明白，有些事情不能勉強，而我可以做的，就是放棄。"}]}